imdb.plot outline: Lucía has moved to a new big city to live with her friend Javier, Paula and Sam, who will help her adapt to this new change. Thanks to webcams that are connected in their house, we open a window to this cyber apartment to get to know the latest trends in music, video games, fashion...etc.
